xul-ext-outlookalike (0.3.0.8-1nano) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream beta release
  * fixed resizing bug. If a long link was hovered in version 0.3.0.7
    the main window of thunderbrird resized itself to be able to show
    the full link. This behavior has been removed.

